  <titles>
    <title type="short" as="introduced">Emergency Aid to Homeless Families Act</title>
    <title type="official" as="introduced">A bill to amend part A of title IV of the Social Security Act to permit States, with Federal matching under the program of emergency assistance to needy families with children, to purchase, construct, renovate, or rent facilities to provide emergency shelter for such families.</title>
